# Keel structure demo — real output from /keel:init on a Go + Chi project

Output demo/structure.gif
Output demo/structure.mp4

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 580
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 24
Set TypingSpeed 65ms

Hide
Type "PS1='$ ' ; cd /tmp/test-keel ; clear"
Enter
Sleep 600ms
Show

Type "tree -a --noreport -I '.git|.DS_Store|demo'"
Enter
Sleep 1800ms

Type "cat .keel/config.yaml"
Enter
Sleep 1800ms

Type "head -10 .claude/rules/go.md"
Enter
Sleep 1800ms

Type "cat docs/soul.md"
Enter
Sleep 3000ms
